data.description: This beautiful, spacious home in Maumelle Valley Estates has distinctive architectural features, abundant storage and lives like a one-level. It features hardwood floors, tray ceilings, custom built-ins and recessed wall niches. On the main level are the primary bedroom suite with its spa-like bath, two more bedrooms with a jack-and-jill bath and a bonus den/game room with a wet bar. The bonus room could also serve as a 5th bedroom. The large eat-in kitchen has granite counters, stained wood cabinets and a pantry with a unique ribbed-glass door. A gas-log fireplace and handsome wood mantle are the focal point of the large living room which is open to the kitchen and dining room. A roomy bedroom suite upstairs is a private spot for in-laws, guests or teens. Outside is a screened-in porch that overlooks the flat backyard and there's easy access to the walking trail just beyond the back fence. One brand new AC unit. Roof and hot water heater are approx 3 years old. Assumable loan at 2.875 for qualified VA buyers.
